history.content: Hi, enrollment hasn't opened up yet but I was just wondering how can I correctly enroll in these two classes when it does open up? 162 and 16b are scheduled for the same lecture time slot, but I believe 162 allows time conflicts while 16b does not. Thus, I was thinking to first enroll in 16b, and then enroll in 162 (all in phase 1). However, I will be a junior in the fall, and it appears that even if there are open seats in 16b during my phase 1, I will automatically be put on the waitlist. Thus, if I continue to add 162 in phase 1, I'm thinking the scheduler won't allow me to get into 16b even off the waitlist? Is there someone I should email to be able to allow this conflict? Thanks.
history.subject: Enrolling in 16B and 162
